          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "As 165Er has no gamma line, it was quantified by the",
                "characteristic X-ray line of its decay product 165Ho.",
                "The 165Er activity was determined from spectra",
                "measured after the total decay of 161Er and 163Er,",
                "ensuring that also the signals from the directly",
                "produced 161-164Ho isomers had disappeared.",
                "To determine the activities in addition to the well",
                "known corrections for pile-up and background in the",
                "low energy region, the self-absorption of the 165Ho",
                "X-rays in the target material were also taken into",
                "account."
              ]
            }
          ],
